Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:37.42,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an9\fs50\blur3\3c&H000000&\bord2}再次开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.08,0:23:52.68,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an9\fs50\blur3\3c&H000000&\bord2}颤抖的心灵 预感到悲剧的来临
